
--Unix--

sudo apt install telnet

telnet towel.blinkenlights.nl


--MacOS--

Install using the following commands 


Install Homebrew 

/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)" brew install telnet


- Once the installation is complete, you can run the infamous "telnet towel" command as usual:


telnet towel.blinkenlights.nl


******Please note that Telnet was removed from macOS with Catalina, so using Homebrew is the recommended method for installing it on newer versions of macOS********
